    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-02-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-02-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="494" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d494">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-02-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 23,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>On information from British ambassador that Americans at Bitlis fear
                            attack, I demanded at Porte telegraphic order for protection, which was
                            promptly sent.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
